trend_summary: From the first to last scene, woodland gives way to expanding subdivisions radiating from the central core. Residential streets infill vacant parcels, new commercial blocks rise east-central, and a widened arterial corridor bisects north-south. Forest edges shrink, while sports fields and lakeside parkland persist, confirming steady suburban consolidation.
